    <item>
      <title>Version 0.1.3</title>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 12:34:03 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.1.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's new in 0.1.3</h2><ul><li>The application bundle is now named <strong>Synapse Meetings.app</strong> (with a space) instead of <code>SynapseMeetings.app</code>. Finder, Dock, and ⌘-Tab will now display the spaced name correctly.</li></ul><p><strong>One-time cleanup:</strong> if you previously installed 0.1.0–0.1.2, the old <code>SynapseMeetings.app</code> may remain in /Applications alongside the new <code>Synapse Meetings.app</code>. You can drag the old one to the Trash.</p>]]></description>
      <enclosure
        url="https://github.com/dep/synapse-meetings/releases/download/0.1.3/SynapseMeetings-0.1.3.dmg"
        sparkle:edSignature="IzCRCELV4oTrTs8TO+s3UclUVTDGbJsLSvxy234YKyTtCYvXFiSqCpvMGdn+E022WXW1k6Z3WfeeKVelO4pLBA=="
