      <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's new in 0.1.2</h2><ul><li>Finder, Dock, and ⌘-Tab now display the app as &ldquo;Synapse Meetings&rdquo; (with a space). The 0.1.1 fix only updated the in-app menu bar; this release adds the localized <code>InfoPlist.strings</code> that Finder actually reads.</li></ul>]]></description>
